cff-version: 1.2.0
message: If you use this work, please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
title: Network Packet‑Rate and Size Latency with Energy Monitoring
abstract: The dataset records latency and energy consumption for a network device
  under test while varying packet rate and size. A libmoon forwarder and MoonGen load
  generator generate traffic, with synchronized runs across two nodes to capture per‑packet
  latency histograms and continuous power usage. Results are aggregated into CSV tables
  and PNG plots, enabling evaluation of throughput‑latency trade‑offs and energy efficiency
  across multiple configurations.
